Company Overview of Arkwin Industries Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Arkwin Industries Inc. designs, engineers, manufactures, and supports hydraulic and fuel system components for commercial aerospace, defense, maritime, and industrial markets. The company offers linear actuators, including utility, engine, and ram air turbine actuators; reservoirs, such as self-pressurizing and gas pressurized reservoirs; dampers, including rotary, piston, and brake master cylinder dampers; control valves, such as utility, directional control, and fire resistant/fire proof valves; and integrated assemblies. Its products are used in fixed-wing aircraft, helicopters, spacecraft, turbine engines, and other applications. The company was founded in 1951 and is based in Westbury, ...
Arkwin Industries Inc. designs, engineers, manufactures, and supports hydraulic and fuel system components for commercial aerospace, defense, maritime, and industrial markets. The company offers linear actuators, including utility, engine, and ram air turbine actuators; reservoirs, such as self-pressurizing and gas pressurized reservoirs; dampers, including rotary, piston, and brake master cylinder dampers; control valves, such as utility, directional control, and fire resistant/fire proof valves; and integrated assemblies. Its products are used in fixed-wing aircraft, helicopters, spacecraft, turbine engines, and other applications. The company was founded in 1951 and is based in Westbury, New York. Arkwin Industries Inc. operates as a subsidiary of TransDigm Inc.
