Arkwin Industries Inc. Key Developments

Derco Aerospace, Inc. Signs Exclusive Distribution Agreement with Arkwin Industries, Inc
Oct 24 16
Derco Aerospace, Inc. announced that it signed a distribution agreement with Arkwin Industries, Inc. as the exclusive provider of Arkwin materials to international customers effective January 1, 2017. With this authorization, Derco will distribute Arkwin products across multiple military platforms to all customers located outside of the United States and Japan.


